TextEng: Yes, I am <FirstName>.
You right. Me name be <FirstName>.
Aribeth? Have you spoken to her recently?
Aribeth? When you speak at her?
Is the battle over then?
Do you know who attacked the Academy?
So what happens now?
Fight over now?
You find out who bad guys be?
What we do now?
I will help you in this task, Fenthick.
Would there be some type of reward for recovering the missing creatures?
Aribeth promised me a reward earlier. I'm still waiting for it.
Text: 아리베스가 전에 보상을 약속했어요. 아직 받지 못했는데요.

TextEng: I suppose my work here is done. I'll be going now.
Text: 제 일은 여기서 끝난 것 같네요. 이제 가보겠습니다.

TextEng: Me want help you, Fenthick.
You gonna give lots gold if me get monsters back?
Text: 나 괴물들 다시 찾아오면 너 금화 많이 줘?

TextEng: Aribeth already promise me reward, but me not get it yet.
Text: 아리베스 이미 나한테 보상 약속했어. 근데 아직 안 받았어.

TextEng: Me guess me done here. Me go now.
Text: 나 여기서 끝난 것 같아. 나 이제 가.

TextEng: I'm not interested.
Me not interested.
You have no right to do this!
Given the choices, I guess I'll help you.
You not got no right for do this!
Me got no choice - me help you.
Text: 나 선택 없어 - 나 너 도와줄게.

TextEng: I wish to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you stuff.
I will meet you at the Halls of Justice within the week then.
Text: 그럼 일주일 안에 정의의 전당에서 뵙겠습니다.

TextEng: Me meet yous at Justice place in the week, then.
Text: 나 일주일 안에 정의 장소에서 볼게.

TextEng: Tell me about yourself.
Tell me about Aribeth.
Tell me about Desther.
Me want know stuff 'bout you.
Me want know stuff 'bout Aribeth.
Me want know stuff 'bout Desther.
Tell me more about these Waterdhavian creatures.
Text: 이 워터딥 생명체들에 대해 더 말해 주세요.

TextEng: Me want know more 'bout Waterdeep monsters.
Text: 나 워터딥 괴물들에 대해 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: So you and Aribeth are lovers?
You and Aribeth be all lovey?
I have come from Lady Aribeth. She sent me to protect the creatures.
Text: 아리베스 경이 보내셨습니다. 생명체들을 보호하라고 저를 보냈어요.

TextEng: Me come from Lady Aribeth. She send me for save creatures.
Text: 나 아리베스 경한테서 왔어. 그녀가 나보고 생명체들 구하라고 보냈어.
